    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/227ddf1267b0ee0f6bce8de35a416a24.webp?t=1767680499\" width=780 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/3fd0c3d4f0486b6a0f6866acfe7be7ce.poster.avif?t=1767680499\" width=1170 height=502 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/3fd0c3d4f0486b6a0f6866acfe7be7ce.webm?t=1767680499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/3fd0c3d4f0486b6a0f6866acfe7be7ce.mp4?t=1767680499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时钟持续转动，但你拥有随心所欲操纵和扭曲时间的力量！每一分、每一秒都将成为你的武器。<br>通过成千上万的反复挑战，完美掌握驾驭时间的奥秘吧！<br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/865a707384844567068a1cab9a8b3f48.webp?t=1767680499\" width=780 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/01777d153a1e62897f709aa6870a3e5b.poster.avif?t=1767680499\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/01777d153a1e62897f709aa6870a3e5b.webm?t=1767680499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁各种技能、技术芯片和特殊能力，蜕变为无人能及的强大存在吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/118ce0512f4b2cdcb0960a21c31bbdaf.webp?t=1767680499\" width=780 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/e4fe1a3fd2e8ddc2136ac033dfece99a.poster.avif?t=1767680499\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/e4fe1a3fd2e8ddc2136ac033dfece99a.webm?t=1767680499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/e4fe1a3fd2e8ddc2136ac033dfece99a.mp4?t=1767680499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升属性，强化强力武器，升级海量装备，成为终极的“时间化身”吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/3d2ef74871b242bfd732e221e9885019.webp?t=1767680499\" width=780 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/5d98ec3ea674a40bd1f3b98c795e752d.poster.avif?t=1767680499\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279910/extras/5d98ec3ea674a40bd1f3b98c795e752d.webm?t=1767680499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >向往极限输出的“玻璃大炮”剑士？那就挥剑斩断眼前的一切阻碍！<br>更偏爱远程作战？那就装弹上膛，在战场上灵活穿梭，向敌人倾泻火力吧！</p>",
